  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This port of Lemmings 2: The Tribes features very similar graphics to the original release, and otherwise plays just about the same. The only differences come via some slight performance downgrades and the soundtrack composed by Mike Clarke which is just a rescored version of the original works made for the SNES soundchip. It also has an easter egg where, if you plug the Super Scope into port two, you can use it to blast the Lemmings.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
